nscription. A sharp crack is heard as jade sparks fly from the scroll*<br>
<br>
To Whom It May Concern:<br>
<br>
                                      I am Kirau, walker of the shadows. I have recently spoke with Baron Vresk on matters of my entrance, and I have his permission to leave this petition for the eyes of the Harvest. I will keep this short...I wish to be among the ranks of the harvest for several reasons...I feel the calling of The Father in my breast, and I can do nothing but heed his call to arms. <br>
                                      My hatred burns deep within my breast, and I wish to make up for my illegitamate birth by slaying as many hethens that stand against the harvest as possible. I am no scholor or philosopher...just a blade in the darkness. A walker of shadows...a warrior of hate, who wishes to find himself among the ranks of the True Army, if it is the Will of the Father. <br>
                                      As I told Vresk, I feel it is my destiny to find salvation from the Harvest, or damnation from the Harvest, and I shall see this prophecy realized, to whatever end The Father would have for me. I will join you, or I will be slain by you. Your actions will dictate the will of the Father. I wish to speak to you all soon, and join you, in servitude to the Father.<br>
                                     Hate with Honor.<br>
                                                           ~Kirau<br>
                                                              22nd Ranger<br>
